## 💡 **WHAT vercel.json DOES:**
```
User visits: /dashboard
               ↓
Vercel: "No /dashboard file... let me check vercel.json"
               ↓
vercel.json: "For ANY route (.*), serve index.html"
               ↓
Serves: index.html (your Vite app)
               ↓
Vite router: "Oh, /dashboard? I'll handle that!"
               ↓
Shows: Dashboard page! ✅
